Subject: drm/i915/display: Wait PSR2 get out of deep sleep to update pipe
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: fed98c16f13f4c68fc507384d3429516ef5c3b6d
